title: How to Shape an Afro Fade | AXE | Instagroom
description:
This is Afro Fade à la Leroy. Crazy but contained. 

THE TOOLS:
AXE Natural Look Softening Cream
Hair pick
Curl sponge

THE STEPS:
1. Pick hair
2. Rub cream into palms
3. Squeeze into hair
4. Sponge for curls

transcripts: Ya, I haven’t seen too many people with the same hair as me. First I use an afro­pick and then I take some cream and squeeze it into my hair. Then I get a sponge and I do it in small circular motion till I have the right size curls that I want. It looks crazy, but like contained.
